Class UCMPlayer

java.lang.Object

      EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemSS
          teams.ucmTeam.UCMPlayer

public abstract class UCMPlayer
extends EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemSS

UCMPlayer is a Control System that represents a robot based on predefined behaviours. All team players share a team manager.

UCMPlayer is an abstract class. To use it you must extend this class and implement the getTeamManager method.

See Also:
Behaviour, TeamManager

Method Detail

Configure

public final void Configure()
Configures the team and the robot. The first time it is invoked it creates and configure the team manager. The team manager is obtained with the getTeamManager(). Then it configures each robot using the default behaviours provided by the team manager.

Overrides:
Configure in class EDU.gatech.cc.is.abstractrobot.ControlSystemS

createTeamManager

protected abstract TeamManager createTeamManager()
Creates a reference to the TeamManager. This method will be called only once during the configuration of all the player that belong to a team.

This method must be implemented by subclasses

Returns:
the team manager that will control the team.
